@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_majldl(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v1
    v0 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.27) - wp.cos(v0 + 0.16)) * wp.exp(wp.abs(tmp + 0.73)))
    v0 = wp.sin(v0)
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.sin(v1 + 0.47)) - (wp.abs(v1 + 0.18) * wp.sin(v1 + 0.98)))
    v1 = ((0.70 * v1) / wp.exp(wp.exp(v0 + 0.72)))
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.19) * (v0 + 0.77 + v1 + 0.06)) + ((v2 + 0.05 - tmp + 0.38) + (v2 + 0.48 / v0 + 0.47)))
    tmp = v0
    v1 = 0.45
    data[tid] = v0
